JONATHAN ZITTRAIN: In both
the book and the presentation,

01:03:42.730 --> 01:03:45.270
you've managed to kind
of capture your optimism

01:03:45.270 --> 01:03:48.300
without being
pollyannish about really

01:03:48.300 --> 01:03:52.150
what's so valuable about the
library and the community

01:03:52.150 --> 01:03:53.640
it represents.

01:03:53.640 --> 01:03:58.140
But you also manage
to put in at least

01:03:58.140 --> 01:04:00.360
two potential snakes
in the gardens that

01:04:00.360 --> 01:04:03.140
are really worrisome.

